<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>SSRF - Vulnerable Lab</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-container">
    <div class="py-4">
      <h1 class="mb-2">Server-Side Request Forgery (SSRF)</h1>
      <p class="text-muted">This demo fetches a URL provided by the user without validation — it can be used to reach internal services.</p>

      <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5>What to try</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Try fetching <code>http://localhost:3000</code> or other internal endpoints.</li>
            <li>Observe responses returned from the server.</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/fetch" class="btn btn-primary">Open Fetch Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-link">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
